  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a first-person walking simulator where players relive paranormal encounters connected to the haunted location known as \"Lantern House\" and uncover the truth behind the events that took place there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3561460/extras/5d5943596735b7a55fd68e7fc1a2f8d8.avif?t=1761827974\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The place called \"DOORS\" offers the collection and reliving of paranormal experiences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There, you are led to a single door.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3561460/extras/72ddbebc0e913c6cd99f2b5d68d78fc4.avif?t=1761827974\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It was the room of a person who had been investigating the haunted location known as \"Lantern House.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3561460/extras/56213627fead8eea1f1c99a9073273a6.avif?t=1761827974\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the player relives several collected eerie tales, they analyze and uncover what truly happened there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・<strong>Genre</strong>: Walking Simulator / Atmospheric Horror</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・<strong>Ending</strong>: 1 ending</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・<strong>Gameplay Duration</strong>: 30 to 60 minutes</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a first-person walking simulator where players relive paranormal encounters connected to the haunted location known as \"Lantern House\" and uncover the truth behind the events that took place there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3561460/extras/5d5943596735b7a55fd68e7fc1a2f8d8.avif?t=1761827974\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The place called \"DOORS\" offers the collection and reliving of paranormal experiences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There, you are led to a single door.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3561460/extras/72ddbebc0e913c6cd99f2b5d68d78fc4.avif?t=1761827974\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It was the room of a person who had been investigating the haunted location known as \"Lantern House.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3561460/extras/56213627fead8eea1f1c99a9073273a6.avif?t=1761827974\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the player relives several collected eerie tales, they analyze and uncover what truly happened there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・<strong>Genre</strong>: Walking Simulator / Atmospheric Horror</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・<strong>Ending</strong>: 1 ending</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・<strong>Gameplay Duration</strong>: 30 to 60 minutes</p>",
